5.title: 3D Secure
5.summary: Verified by Visa (VbV), MasterCard SecureCode, and AMEX SafeKey are security features that prompt customers to enter a  passcode when they pay by Visa, MasterCard, or AMEX. Merchants that want to integrate VbV, SecureCode, or SafeKey must  have signed up for the service through their bank merchant account issuer. This service must also be enabled by our  support team.

23.title: Masterpass
23.summary: You can use Masterpass to integrate Mastercard’s digital payment service with Bambora’s payment gateway. Masterpass is a digital payment service where consumers can store card information for Visa, Mastercard, Discover, and American Express. Masterpass provides quick integration for merchants to accept payments from these card holders.
